rating_comment:
I must say the picture put on the Airbnb site does not do justice to Md's place. This apartment is really spacious with four full bedroom, dining space, full living room with a tons of sitting arrangement. There is a fully equipped kitchen with different new cooking tools. There are three full bathrooms, two attached with two bedrooms and one in common area. That bathroom is huge with a bathtub inside of it. All the bathrooms has both high comod and regular bengali shitter. Common bathroom has a sink inside and a sink outside. Outside sink is close to the dining room, makes it convenient to use. Two bedroom with attached bathroom also had their attached varanda. The House is excellent for a staycation in the busy city like Dhaka with family. Both caretaker and the cleaning lady were helpful and kind. Staying in this place was worth every penny. It made us feel like staying in home, away from home.
I HIGHLY recommend this place to anyone for their staycation, or family gettogether.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · September 2023,  · Stayed about a week
rating_comment: It was a nice and very comfy stay, host was very friendly and the house not only the perfect location but also clean and tidy house. It had everything you need for a short stay. I stayed with my family and we all loved it. Property was close to a the local shops which was helpful and the cleaner & caretaker was very helpful, will be always my first priority whenever I need stay in dhaka, highly recommend for other people also.

A very nice house, felt like my own home, I got very homely feelings,
The location is absolutely peak location, everything is available at hand, the market is two minutes away
And the environment of the house and the surrounding environment was also good..
